m0NESY
On his path to "baby GOAT" status, m0NESY reached 7,000 FACEIT Elo in CS:GO, over 10% higher then the next highest player. At just 14, he joined FACEIT Pro League as its second youngest participant. G2 Esports signed him after honing his skills in FPL, and in 2023, he became a champion at both IEM Katowice and IEM Cologne 2023.
